<title>ʿjz lsạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ʿjz lsạny ʿn ạltʿbyr .. lmạ nwyt ạ̉wṣf yswʿ)2
 (ḥạwlt ạ̉smw bạltfkyr .. nṭq fw̉ạdy wqạl yạ jmwʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (yạ rytny ạ̉qdr ạ̉qwl wạ̉ʿbr)2 .. ʿn ạ̉wṣạf ạlrb yswʿ
 yạ rytny ạ̉qdr ạ̉qwl wạ̉ʿbr .. ʿn ạ̉wṣạf ạlrb yswʿ
 2- (blḥẓẗ wạḥdẗ fy ṭrfẗ ʿyn .. ṭhrny dmh ṣrt sʿyd)2
 (ṭwbạk yạ qlby bqyt mlyạn .. frḥ lạ ynṭq bh wmjyd)2
 3- (lmạ ḍʿft fy ạlṭryq .. ạlʿdw kẖdny fy ạlẓlmạt)2
 (lqyt yswʿ ạ̉wfy̱ ṣdyq .. sḥq ʿdwy wqạl hyhạt)2
 3- (qdws ạ̹lhy yswʿ ạlbạr .. mjdaⁿạ lṣạḥb ạlạ̉mjạd)2
 (ṭwbạk yạ mw̉mn yạ mkẖtạr .. htʿysẖ fy ẓlh llạ̉bd)2</lyrics>
</song>